etomica.virial

Class BnJHBVArgon_Analytic

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.virial.BnJHBVArgon_Analytic

  • public class BnJHBVArgon_Analytic
extends java.lang.Object
    Computes virial coefficients for argon using the analytical expressions developed by Jaeger, Hellmann, Bich, and Vogel (2011), JCP, 135: 084308. The authors computed B4-B7 using MSMC. They employed only a pair potential and a nonadditive trimer potential, the later of which they developed in this work. The potentials are ab initio. A first-order quantum correction is included on B2-B4. The nonadditive trimer contribution to B7 is neglected.
